## ğŸ§© Serializers

### ListingSerializer

Serializes all fields of the `Listing` model. The following fields are **read-only**:
- `created_at`
- `updated_at`
- `listing_id`

### BookingSerializer

Serializes all fields of the `Booking` model. The following fields are **read-only**:
- `created_at`
- `booking_id`

